project.name: Symbiote Evolutionary NFT
project.description: Symbiote is a dynamic evolutionary NFT and autonomous on-chain companion. It acts as a "pet strategist," learning your wallet behavior to plan financial actions and route Jupiter trades. After every verified outcome, it autonomously evolves its Level, XP, and Personality. A living game character and financial operator on Solana.
project.solanaIntegration: Uses Solana for on-chain swaps via Jupiter and evolves NFT state on-chain based on outcomes.
